**Date:** 2025-04-08

**Type:** [FIX]

**Author:** Development Team



<h2>Changes</h2>



<ul><li>Fixed markdown rendering in the documentation viewer</li></ul>

<ul><li>Added dedicated CSS for the markdown viewer</li></ul>

<ul><li>Improved section display and collapsible content</li></ul>

<ul><li>Fixed CSS path references in the markdown viewer template</li></ul>



<h2>Motivation</h2>



The documentation system was not correctly displaying markdown content, particularly for the Documentation_Workflow.md file. The content was visible but sections were not properly formatted and details were not accessible through button clicks.



<h2>Impact</h2>



<ul><li>Improved readability of documentation pages</li></ul>

<ul><li>Fixed section collapsing/expanding functionality</li></ul>

<ul><li>Enhanced overall user experience when viewing documentation</li></ul>

<ul><li>Ensured all documentation content is properly displayed and accessible</li></ul>

